{"tid":105644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國世紀】IIF:中國去年資本流出7250億美元　創紀錄","createTime":"2017-02-03T05:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T05:13:04.000Z","uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6baedc5c6d0b3932efbf79a9de8cc13c7de3a8e0","tid":105644,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IIF:中國去年資本流出7250億美元 創紀錄</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/02/03/1484864_262c92a9ae6e04445160a3ec720d270e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F1484864_262c92a9ae6e04445160a3ec720d270e.jpg&h=90a25e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際金融協會(IIF)表示，去年中國資本流出大幅增長，創下7250億美元的紀錄，<strong>如果美國企業因為政治壓力而將獲利滙回國內，中國資本外流還將進一步加劇。</strong><br />\n<br />\nIIF估計，<strong>中國去年資本淨流出比2015年增加500億美元，遠高於其他新興經濟體的資本流入。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2014年中國資本淨流出僅為1600億美元。</strong>過去兩年中國國內企業和居民的資本加速出逃，部分因為人民幣兌美元的貶值預期。<br />\n<br />\n資本流出導致去年中國外滙儲備下降3200億美元，促使當局收緊資本控制。人民幣兌美元去年貶值6.5%，為歷來貶值幅度最大的一年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1484864/IIF%3A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA7250%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1484864%2FIIF%253A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2587%25BA7250%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%2B%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=62d38ae4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1484864/IIF%3A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA7250%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84</a>"},{"pid":"8dba5b96418ab619506cb2df4f6a121a86423372","tid":105644,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"不斷印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}